#

Garlic Butter Shrimp Pasta

25 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

ShellfishGluten

Dietary Tags:

SeafoodPastaQuick Meal

Cuisine:

ItalianAmerican

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

Easy30-Minute MealsPasta Dishes

Description

A quick and flavorful pasta dish featuring succulent shrimp in a rich garlic butter sauce, perfect for a weeknight dinner.

Ingredients

  • spaghetti or linguine: 8 oz
  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 lb
  • butter: 4 tbsp
  • garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • parsley (chopped): 2 tbsp
  • lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • red pepper flakes (optional): 1/2 tsp
